You're all professional chefs?

00:12:35.820 --> 00:12:37.320
Yes, question?

00:12:37.320 --> 00:12:40.410
Well, I mean, in the finale of
"Next Iron Chef," which I was

00:12:40.410 --> 00:12:41.370
in, and I lost.

