I don't have six more weeks.

00:14:56.240 --> 00:14:58.280
It's just a long time
commitment.

00:14:58.280 --> 00:15:00.080
And to be honest, been
there, done that.

00:15:00.080 --> 00:15:02.060
It was fun to do.

