sharing than cooking.

00:43:40.660 --> 00:43:42.790
And if you're a father or
mother or a boyfriend,

00:43:42.790 --> 00:43:45.960
girlfriend, and you actually
cook for your spouse or your

00:43:45.960 --> 00:43:48.320
family, you're giving
something.

00:43:48.320 --> 00:43:51.820
And it's cliche, but you
are giving your love.

00:43:51.820 --> 00:43:56.710
You're giving part of
you and offering it.

00:43:56.710 --> 00:44:00.300
And it doesn't take that much
skill if you just follow a

00:44:00.300 --> 00:44:01.790
basic recipe.

