I mean, I don't know how many
kids-- you know, yeah,

00:44:26.730 --> 00:44:28.380
Brussels sprouts, high
five, you know?

00:44:28.380 --> 00:44:29.960
Because they know it's
going to be coated

00:44:29.960 --> 00:44:30.980
