Angiogenesis is something
naturally

00:46:37.130 --> 00:46:38.150
occurring in your body.

00:46:38.150 --> 00:46:42.130
Menstruation, placenta creation,
scab formation is

00:46:42.130 --> 00:46:42.430
angiogenesis.

00:46:42.430 --> 00:46:44.910
You need it balanced
and you're fine.

00:46:44.910 --> 00:46:49.010
When it's imbalanced by a bad
diet, the blood vessels go to

00:46:49.010 --> 00:46:51.750
